<a href="/questions/663101-i-can-t-find-the-edition-i-have-on">I can&#39;t find the edition I have on Goodreads: the cover is like this one but instead of a banana it has a sausage with a fly on it and there&#39;s a little &quot;Master Chefs&quot; label on the sausage. Does anyone else have the same edition as me?</a>
